headline: A Nuclear Power Play And TurboTax Stock Reach New Highs
summary: While the general market saw weakness Friday ahead of a three-day weekend, Intuit stock and GE Vernova each reached fresh new highs. GE Vernova stock got a boost as nuclear names rallied on news President Donald Trump is expected to sign executive orders Friday to support the nuclear energy sector.
